---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Boat & Ice Fishing Rigging Calculators"
  description="Free calculators for trolling motor sizing, battery runtime, prop pitch, outboard HP limits, livewell aeration, anchor scope, and downrigger letback. Built for anglers."
>
  <div class="panel-head">
    <div>
      <h1>Rigging Math, <span class="accent">Not Guesswork</span></h1>
      <p>Free calculators built from real spec sheets and the actual USCG formula — not generic rules of thumb recycled from forum posts. No signup. No ads on the tool. Pick a calculator above.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <article class="guide">
    <p>Every calculator on this site is built to be used on the water, on your phone, with the boat already loaded — not just browsed once and forgotten. Start with <a href="/boat-power/" style="color:var(--sonar)">trolling motor sizing</a> if you're rigging electric power, <a href="/outboard-specs/" style="color:var(--sonar)">outboard specs</a> if you're shopping motors, or <a href="/ice-power/" style="color:var(--sonar)">ice power</a> if you're planning a hard-water trip.</p>

    <h2>Guides</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="/guides/12v-vs-24v-vs-36v-trolling-motors/" style="color:var(--sonar)">12V vs 24V vs 36V Trolling Motors Explained</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/series-vs-parallel-battery-wiring/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Series vs Parallel Battery Wiring</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/lithium-vs-lead-acid-ice-fishing/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Lithium vs Lead-Acid for Ice Fishing</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/understanding-prop-slip/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Understanding Prop Slip</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/choosing-the-right-prop-pitch/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Choosing the Right Prop Pitch</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/uscg-horsepower-formula-explained/" style="color:var(--sonar)">How the USCG Horsepower Formula Works</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/livewell-water-temperature-fish-survival/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Livewell Water Temperature and Fish Survival</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/anchor-scope-explained/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Anchor Scope, Explained</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/chain-vs-rope-anchor-rode/" style="color:var(--sonar)">Chain vs Rope Anchor Rode</a><br/>
      <a href="/guides/how-downrigger-blowback-works/" style="color:var(--sonar)">How Downrigger Blowback Works</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
